Write code to check whether a variable i is even.
The code should change the value of variable iseven to 1 if i is even, otherwise 0.
int i;      /* Variable whose value is to be checked */
int iseven;  /* Variable to store 1 if i is even and 0 otherwise */

/* Write Code to load 1 in variable iseven if variable i is even, 0 otherwise */
if(i%2==0) iseven=1;
else iseven=0;




 
